title: Dead Europe
description: In Greece to scatter his father's ashes, Isaac hears of a curse that hangs over the head of his family. Dismissing the idea, his trip begins to unveil dark truths that forced his father to flee years ago. (2012)
description2: In Greece to scatter his father's ashes, Isaac hears of a curse that hangs over the head of his family. Dismissing the idea, his trip begins to unveil dark truths that forced his father to flee years ago.

title: Bob & Carol & Ted & Alice
description: A married couple swept up with the idea of free love, convince their friends, another married couple, to join them. As their dalliance grows, unspoken tensions begin to surface between them. (1969)
description2: A married couple swept up with the idea of free love, convince their friends, another married couple, to join them. As their dalliance grows, unspoken tensions begin to surface between them.

title: Pollock
description: The story of an extraordinary artist, Pollock, struggling with self doubt whilst caught up in a tug of war between the need to express himself and wanting to shut the world out. (2000)
description2: The story of an extraordinary artist, Pollock, struggling with self doubt whilst caught up in a tug of war between the need to express himself and wanting to shut the world out.

title: Pecking Order
description: Fierce rivalries, club infighting, problematic birds and irregular judging are just some of the challenges faced by a group of zealous Kiwi chicken breeders hell bent on victory at the 2015 National Poultry Show. (2017)
description2: Fierce rivalries, club infighting, problematic birds and irregular judging are just some of the challenges faced by a group of zealous Kiwi chicken breeders hell bent on victory at the 2015 National Poultry Show.

title: Catching A Predator
description: The inside story of the investigation into serial male rapist Reynhard Sinaga and the biggest rape case in British legal history. Sexual violence against men remains one of the most underreported crimes.
description2: The inside story of the investigation into serial male rapist Reynhard Sinaga and the biggest rape case in British legal history. Sexual violence against men remains one of the most underreported crimes.

title: Crowded House Live At Sydney Opera House
